          <a href="#title2-2-1" class="list-group-item">　　<small><i class="fa fa-play-circle"></i>　初回のお支払い</small></a>
          <a href="#title2-2-2" class="list-group-item">　　<small><i class="fa fa-play-circle"></i>　閲覧期間の延長</small></a>
